translated: Michelsen, Otto William, director, Alingsås, b. 17/10/94 in Alingsås to editor William M. and Alma Virginia Beckmark. M. 22 with Ingeborg Kerstin Holmlund. Children: Ingrid b. 23, Bengt b. 27, Gunvor b. 31. — Studied at Allingsås s’anTsk., then in gymnasium class at Gbgs sam’sk. Special studies: traveled for six months in Germany and Austria in '21. Executive director at A-B William Michelsen's printing press and responsible for Alingsås Tidning and Elfsborgs Läns Tidning since '30. Member of the Publishers' Club and Swedish Newspaper Publishers Association since '23, as well as the Göta Association and Freemasons Order.
